{"tid":999274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"謝絕左本土　泛民收緊皮　建制派都差唔多時辰到了","createTime":"2019-01-28T14:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T04:48:29.000Z","uid":47714,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"baaad2ddf2c15954f1e3bd7d17b7650215feeb53","tid":999274,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:49:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1089586340587462656\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1089586340587462656&d=lCA45G8Nzi7RNDaJePiRJwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=c11a5b3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1089586340587462656&h=55e98424\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1089586340587462656</a><br />\n<br />\n阻截了泛本土，泛民也已廢掉並步向凋亡，所謂建制派其實已沒有用了罷。那電視劇所謂某政黨領袖參選，不現實。政治家或者政客，是生存和生活在政治市場之中的人，是市場人士的一種。而從董建華、梁振英去看，加上曾蔭權、林鄭月娥，是另一批人。他們一直說是行政主導，可能有人還未明是怎樣。"},{"pid":"bc978e18fda01dd58454a1c9561c2693433705ee","tid":999274,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d18acd6baaa8407a85a974f4ef65dde0adcc620","tid":999274,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T18:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0adfb83c0874071889ef570c6214b6b8a34ded","tid":999274,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T21:02:44.000Z","msg":"始終要搵人交戲投票"},{"pid":"e5de95f06c6af2757a1c7b77a8d514ac037705dd","tid":999274,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7983f9265e86639b46964bf4dbf36431c470ce68","tid":999274,"uid":192517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04: